<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Maintenance Mode | MyCarRepair</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/favicon.png">
    <style>
        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 15% 20%, #1e3a8a 0, #0f172a 55%, #020617 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .maintenance-card {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 520px;
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.72);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
            border-radius: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.45);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            text-align: center;
            padding: 34px 28px;
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.2);
            color: #fdba74;
            border: 1px solid rgba(251, 146, 60, 0.45);
            border-radius: 999px;
            padding: 8px 14px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.4px;
            margin-bottom: 14px;
        }

        h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 34px;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -0.6px;
        }

        p {
            margin: 14px 0 0;
            color: #cbd5e1;
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        .action {
            margin-top: 26px;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            background: #f97316;
            color: white;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <main class="maintenance-card">
        <div class="badge">System Update in Progress</div>
        <h1>We will be back shortly</h1>
        <p>
            MyCarRepair is currently under maintenance to improve reliability and performance.
            Please check back in a few minutes.
        </p>
        <!-- <a class="action" href="/staff-portal">Staff Portal</a> -->
    </main>
</body>
</html>
